description:
Everyone deserves to feel safe and free from harm. However, home is not always a safe place to be. In Australia, on average, one woman is killed every week by a current or former partner – often at home. The statistics in New Zealand are equally disturbing. How do we respond to this alarming situation? Is there a solution? Is there anything we can do?
